as you may know siebert cisneros shank  co llc scs and national financial services llc nfs have an agreement in which nfs provides trade execution clearing and other related services for your brokerage account we want you to know that nfs has an extensive plan in place to complete your transactions with us and to protect your account information in the event of a business disruption please review nfs’ business continuity statement which is shown below for more details communication with our customers is critical to our business we have multiple means of accessing bloomberg as well as multiple sales offices so we can continue to provide superior service even in the event of a business disruption for municipal issuers scs has redundant facilities with underwriting centers located in oakland ca and new york ny as well as redundant technological means to access our underwriting system these safeguards ensure that in the event of a business disruption in either location we will be able to bring your new issue to market and as noted above we will be able to maintain contact with our institutional buyers during such an event other disclosures privacy notice antimoney laundering notice complaint procedure and sipc informationdownload the nfs business continuity plan  6 siebert cisneros shank  co llc  member finra and sipc home services   investment banking  underwriting public finance corporate sales  trading financial advisory services research  market analyses about   about our firm our team community involvement experience   sector experience airports  seaports corporates education general obligation statelevel transportation water  sewer other experience case studies rankings news  media contact us   locations careers request info home  siebert cisneros shank  co llc submit siebert cisneros shank serves new york city municipal water finance authority as senior manager on  million current refunding learn more the  million series a go bonds price at the tightest spreads e