al properties will lead the corporate banking sales and trading teams and continue the expansion of scsco’s corporate finance presence read more   see all news articles and press releases credit market updatedownload our latest market reports get report upcoming dealssee our current and upcoming transactions see list sector experienceairports  seaportsgeneral obligationtransportationwater  sewer see more  6 siebert cisneros shank  co llc  member finra and sipc home services   investment banking  underwriting public finance corporate sales  trading financial advisory services research  market analyses about   about our firm our team community involvement experience   sector experience airports  seaports corporates education general obligation statelevel transportation water  sewer other experience case studies rankings news  media contact us   locations careers request info disclosures  siebert cisneros shank  co llc submit disclosures business continuity plan siebert cisneros shank  co llc — business continuity plan for institutional customers as you may know siebert cisneros shank  co llc scs and national financial services llc nfs have an agreement in which nfs provides trade execution clearing and other related services for your brokerage account we want you to know that nfs has an extensive plan in place to complete your transactions with us and to protect your account information in the event of a business disruption please review nfs’ business continuity statement which is shown below for more details communication with our customers is critical to our business we have multiple means of accessing bloomberg as well as multiple sales offices so we can continue to provide superior service even in the event of a business disruption for municipal issuers scs has redundant facilities with underwriting centers located in oakland ca and new york ny as well as redundant technological means to access our underwriting system these safeguards ensure that in the event of a